        <h2>Pricing: BetterHelp vs Talkspace</h2>
        <p>Both platforms work on a weekly subscription model. Here's how they compare in Australian dollars:</p>
        <p><strong>Talkspace</strong> starts slightly cheaper at around $49 AUD/week for their messaging-only plan. That's about $196/month — marginally easier on the wallet.</p>
        <p><strong>BetterHelp</strong> starts at around $60 AUD/week but includes more — their messaging plan is genuinely unlimited, not the "5 messages a week" cap that some of Talkspace's lower tiers impose.</p>
        <p>On the higher tiers with video sessions included, both platforms converge to similar price points — roughly $80-110 AUD/week depending on your plan.</p>

        <div class="cta-box">
